# Google OAuth 2.0 Client ID — required for Google Sign-In and Drive sync.
#
# Steps to get one:
#   1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
#   2. Create a project (or select an existing one)
#   3. Enable the "Google Drive API"
#   4. Create an OAuth 2.0 Client ID (type: "Web application")
#   5. Add Authorized JavaScript Origins:
#        http://localhost:5173         (Vite dev server)
#        https://your-production-url  (your deployed URL)
#   6. Copy the Client ID below
#
# Copy this file to ".env" and fill in the value:
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your_client_id_here.apps.googleusercontent.com
